original: Lindberg, Karl David, komminister, Vadstena, f. 4/1/07 i Västervik av fabr. C. J. E. L. o. Ida Sofia Linderson. ■— — Stud:ex. i Västervik 26, stud. i Lpps. 28, teol. fil. ex. 30, teol. kand. 33, prästv. f. Linköp. stift 34. Past:-adj. o. v. pastor i V. Ed 34, adj. i Linderås o. v. pastor i Godegård 36, v. pastor i Odensvi 37, kommin. i Järeda o. Virserum 39-43, kommin. i Vadstena sed. 43.
translated:
Lindberg, Karl David, curate, Vadstena, b. 4/1/07 in Västervik to factory worker C.J.E.L. and Ida Sofia Linderson. ■— — High school graduate in Västervik '26, student in Uppsala '28, theology bachelor's degree '30, theology candidate '33, ordained for the Diocese of Linköping '34. Assistant pastor and acting pastor in V. Ed '34, assistant pastor in Linderås and acting pastor in Godegård '36, assistant pastor in Odensvi '37, curate in Järeda and Virserum '39-43, curate in Vadstena since '43. 

Note: '\d\d m. partner's name' indicates that the person got married in the year 19xx.
